{"tid":1573201,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"試著不要再問點贏","createTime":"2019-09-16T02:06:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-16T05:39:23.000Z","uid":205394,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c90b76c834cb87c9ae0073d2311679508f8fc697","tid":1573201,"uid":205394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T02:06:22.000Z","msg":"試著不要再問「點贏？」<br />\n試著問自己「應該做D咩？」<br />\n<br />\n試著不要再問「輸左點算？」<br />\n試著問自己個心「想做D咩？」<br />\n<br />\n我相信咁多位手足都並非投機主義者<br />\n我地最一開始站出來既初衷都係為左我地個心所信所想既信念<br />\n我地係因為覺得應該站出來而站出來<br />\n因為我地個心想去做而做<br />\n<br />\n唔好執著輸贏，成事在人<br />\n貫徹我地既信念<br />\n寧化飛灰 不作浮塵"},{"pid":"9435508721852fda666a0c022845d35b73ec2711","tid":1573201,"uid":205394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T02:08:38.000Z","msg":"（1/10）"},{"pid":"2ff02f821a126bddd99574558299629c2b6c82cb","tid":1573201,"uid":205394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T02:08:49.000Z","msg":"（2/10）"},{"pid":"6df618652ddafc16b0ac2a49b5a6736435c5951c","tid":1573201,"uid":205394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T02:10:23.000Z","msg":"（3/10）"},{"pid":"1526d23203a9ee3a63ea523de232bdfecd236345","tid":1573201,"uid":205394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T02:10:33.000Z","msg":"（4/10）"},{"pid":"c21f947db81314da11d5e4ea99a52db9f622d2c4","tid":1573201,"uid":205394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T02:10:58.000Z","msg":"（5/10）"},{"pid":"cdb1141254b5e0abf2bb71618953c2eb1d8fc2f4","tid":1573201,"uid":215794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T02:11:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c583d7c1afc149146a0974e9e3be3d8bcd3d0fdb","tid":1573201,"uid":205394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T02:17:24.000Z","